Name: Lunarum Bracelet
AttributesDescription: A bracelet given to you by Iuno, once again.
BgDescription: You tried to return it to her. Yet, in time, it found its way back to you. To wear it or keep it safe, the choice is yours, and in that choice lies her trust. But this time, it means something more. No longer merely a relic of her long and lonely journey, it has become proof that you reached out and drew the moon to your side. She Anchored the world, and you, with this, have Anchored her.
ObtainedShowDescription: A bracelet given to you by Iuno, once again. It's like a crescent moon resting on the wrist.
